@startuml
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber "<b>" 0 ""

box "producer" #LightBlue
participant producer as p1
end box

box "consumer" #LightBlue
participant consumer as c1
end box

box "broker" #LightBlue
participant broker as b1
end box

box "NameServer" #LightSkyBlue2
participant NameServer as ns1
participant NameServer as ns2
note right of ns1:green;监听 broker 链接\n监听 producer 链接\n监听 consumer 链接 end note
end box


== <u>NameServer</u>启动流程 == 
p1 -> ns1 :<color:red><size=9>**1** </size></color>启动<b>NameServer服务器</b>\n|||
ns1->ns1:<color:red><size=8>**2 **</size></color>启动监听 |||
activate ns1
deactivate ns1
...3..>>\n||||
